  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To assist the Project Director or Project Engineer in the daily execution of work.</li>\n  <li>To supervise the work of sub-contractors and in-house workers.</li>\n  <li>To work closely with other site operations staff to meet the project schedule.</li>\n  <li>Ensure installation is carried out as per construction drawings.</li>\n  <li>To monitor the progress and quality of work being performed by workers.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that works are executed within an acceptable standard of workmanship.</li>\n  <li>Attend the daily tool-box meeting and convey clear instruction accordingly.</li>\n  <li>Understand and ensure compliance in project requirement and scope of work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 10 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n  <li>Highly proactive attitude, self-motivated, team player, strong problem-solving and communication skills.</li>\n</ul>",
